  <meta name="keywords" content="HTML, CSS, JavaScript"> key words to assit browsers in finding your website...
  <meta name="author" content="John Doe"> let's browser and viewers know who made it
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"> assits with sizing on devices
